This preset intentionally ships only config.env.

It is consumed as the wizard's vault-org fallback layer by
`pa init` (auto-detect mode) — the SKILL.md, daily-template.md, and
README.md that other presets ship are not used in that consumption
path.

If you want to invoke `pa init --preset default` to install a usable
skill for a different Obsidian setup, add those three files. See
presets/obsidian-ce/ for the layout.
